{"tid":843764,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得死好可怕？","createTime":"2018-10-01T11:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T13:04:44.000Z","uid":131181,"like":48,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"80522757c9276aaf072df5735ef5bf948a5c539a","tid":843764,"uid":131181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"每當諗起死個刻，好似熄左電視咁，漆黑一片，再無任何觸感，無任何想法。我好驚，因為會好寂寞，因為就要永遠對住一片無聲既黑暗。每次諗到一到心入面都好辛苦，好難呼吸，眼淚就接住而黎，眼見親人越黎越老就會驚佢地要去面對依一切。死好可怕。依家每日開始都會有依種感覺，好驚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940bad0b52043d7fb7d8b9b8b38983d94c69ce30","tid":843764,"uid":48767,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:38:45.000Z","msg":"你未試過訓覺？"},{"pid":"14993fe2af040594e0394f7080430488e8786d3a","tid":843764,"uid":2411,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"係人都怕死咖啦，話唔怕個啲先on9"},{"pid":"3005289744cf4a9cd2a94d88c03b3f93be112912","tid":843764,"uid":131181,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"940bad0b52043d7fb7d8b9b8b38983d94c69ce30","tid":843764,"uid":48767,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:38:45.000Z","msg":"你未試過訓覺？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:40:17.000Z","msg":"臨瞓前都有驚呀 唔係怕醒唔到 係覺得無夢個段時間好恐怖"},{"pid":"ef4af539213121c58fb569a51042831e1efaced0","tid":843764,"uid":150912,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:41:30.000Z","msg":"我唔驚死<br />\n驚人地死"},{"pid":"85bf08a70dad7f2c978eff58135a12482a047bd3","tid":843764,"uid":131181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14993fe2af040594e0394f7080430488e8786d3a","tid":843764,"uid":2411,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"係人都怕死咖啦，話唔怕個啲先on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime